# ── Build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/bin/
**/obj/
# Local release staging produced by build_release.ps1
/dist/

# ── Visual Studio ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.rsuser
*.userosscache

# ── NuGet ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/packages/
**/project.nuget.cache
**/project.assets.json

# ── Add-in manifests (generated per machine from the .addin.template) ──────────
*.addin

# ── Local runtime data and exported presets ───────────────────────────────────
**/Checkup_Catalogs.json
**/Checkup_Capabilities.json
**/Checkup_Capabilities.json.migrated
Exported_*_Presets.json
# Checkup_Settings.json is tracked: it is the factory seed (StylePurge defaults
# + demo presets). Live user presets are stored in the Windows Registry.

# ── Local sample/test data ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/Resources/Test_Spezifik.*

# ── Obfuscation config and output ─────────────────────────────────────────────
**/Dotfuscator/

# ── Local editor and tooling settings ─────────────────────────────────────────
**/.claude/
CLAUDE.md
/tools/

# ── Inventor interop PIA ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copied per-version from each locally installed Inventor's
# Bin\Public Assemblies\ folder (run fetch_interop.ps1). Never committed —
# it is part of the Autodesk install, not our source. Any machine with the
# matching Inventor version installed can regenerate it.
/lib/**/Autodesk.Inventor.Interop.dll
/lib/Autodesk.Inventor.Interop.dll
